---
layout: base.njk
title: VPNHUB - Tutorials & VPN Guides
description: VPN tutorials, privacy guides, server tips, and video lessons.
---
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="badge">VPN tutorials • Privacy • Server guides</span>
    <h1>Learn VPN, Privacy & Online Security with <span class="highlight">VPNHUB</span></h1>
    <p>Step-by-step tutorials with text, images, and video lessons. Add or edit posts anytime from the Netlify admin panel.</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn" href="/tutorials/">View Tutorials</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="/videos/">Watch Videos</a>
    </div>
   
<div class="cms-note">
  Admin editing is ready: after Netlify setup, open <strong>/admin/</strong> to add or update blog posts.
</div>


  </div>
</header>
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Latest Tutorials</h2>
    <p class="lead">Fresh guides and blog posts from VPNHUB.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | slice(0, 6) %}
      <article class="post-card">
        {% if post.data.image %}<img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">{% endif %}
        <div class="meta">{{ post.data.date }} · {{ post.data.category }}</div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url }}">Read More →</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner grid">
    <div class="card"><h3>Text Tutorials</h3><p>Write detailed setup guides, step-by-step instructions, troubleshooting tips, and privacy advice.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Images</h3><p>Upload screenshots and tutorial images directly from the CMS editor.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h3>Videos</h3><p>Embed YouTube videos or add your own video tutorial links inside posts.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>
